4/18/2021	2013 - Adam Back introduces himself to BitcoinTalk	
4/19/2021	2012 - US Based exchange gets Federally licensed as a MSB	
4/20/2021	2012 - Bitcoinica.com gets licensed as a MSB.
          2013 - Bitcoin Crashes: Bitcoin Central is hacked, with hackers making away with “a few hundred” Bitcoins that the site’s owners agreed to fully cover.	
