4/25/2021	2012 - First Music album sold for bitcoins exclusively – Before being sold on iTunes	
4/26/2021	2012 - First WebCam site to accept Bitcoins[27]. Bitcoins accepted as an alternative payment. Entertainer payouts are not in Bitcoin	
4/27/2021	2011 - VirWoX opens first market to trade Bitcoins against a virtual currency on BTC/SL (Second Life Lindens) exchange.	
